      "span_text": "Finally the Chip Firing Game on a mutating graph (MCFG)  is played on a directed graph that changes during the game in the following way: after the firing of a vertex, its outgoing edges are removed and new ones are added in a pre-determined way (the vertex set V remains the same).",
